General.Name: Monterey Bio Acquisition Corp
General.Description: Monterey Innovation Acquisition Corp. does not have significant operations. It focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, stock purchase, recapitalization, reorganization, or related business combination with one or more businesses in the biotech industry. The company was formerly known as Monterey Bio Acquisition Corporation and changed its name to Monterey Innovation Acquisition Corp. in March 2023. The company was incorporated in 2020 and is based in New York, New York.
